1) install mongoDb, mongoose, express for routing and storage purposes:

2) All the api calls : 

GET: http://localhost:8000/users
GET: http://localhost:8000/users/id   // for a perticular user
POST: http://localhost:8000/users      
PATCH: http://localhost:8000/users/id
DELETE: http://localhost:8000/users/id  // to delete a perticular user from database: